fields.name: SnowBoard Mens: GNU Essential Service Snowboard - Blem 2021
fields.description: C3 Technology – Aggressive dominant cambers out to the contacts combined with mild rocker between your feet. Subtle Banana rocker gives freestyle freedom with maximum end to end stability for big, high-speed lines. For aggressive, skilled riders.

fields.name: SnowBoard Mens: Lib Tech TRS C3 Snowboard - Blem 2021
fields.description: Rip. It. Up. Doesn't matter where you are on the mountain, the Lib Tech TRS C3 Snowboard will lead you to glory. Short for Total Ripper Series, the TRS was originally designed for park and slopestyle, but has become a go-to for aggressive and progressive freestyle all over the mountain. It's a good thing this board comes in many sizes, because the total ripper within you deserves a board of proper shredness.

fields.name: SnowBoard Mens: Lib Tech Skunk Ape HP C2 Snowboard - Blem 2021
fields.description: C2 Technology – Lib Tech worked with Travis Rice to develop this perfectly balanced all terrain contour. Mild rocker between your feet with powerful cambers to the tips and tails. Enough power pop and precision to technically hit the biggest wedges, enough float and freedom to rip the gnarliest AK pow lines. Carves the resort, plays in the park, and slays powder.

fields.name: SnowBoard Mens: Sims Bowl Squad Snowboard 2021
fields.description: If you dream of joining the squad in bigger, badder terrain, you gotta nail the basics first. The Sims Bowl Squad Snowboard is here to help. This soft flexing board is designed to boost skills and confidence for riders just starting out on the journey. It's a lightweight true twin with an all mountain heart - easy turning, playful, and seriously fun to bonk around on in the park and beyond. It does everything you need it to when you're just getting the hang of things, and theres nothing better to take you where you want to go.
